{
    "name": "Hydra",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Hydra",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Variant Hydras",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Scholars of bestial lore can describe several hydra variations. Though rare, hydras with more than five heads live in very isolated areas, sometimes guarding incredibly powerful artifacts. Legendary, 12-headed miasma hydras dwell in horribly polluted and dangerous swamps. Perhaps the most unexpected danger are newly hatched hydra larvae, born hungry in shallow bogs.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Monster Core",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Monster Core pg. 204",
                                "alt": "Monster Core pg. 204",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            },
                            "page": 204,
                            "errata": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "1.1",
                                "alt": "1.1",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "related_creatures",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Related Creatures",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Related Creatures",
                        "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "text": "Hydras are multiheaded, foul-tempered serpentine beasts with voracious appetites, widely feared for their regeneration abilities.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Monster Core",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Monster Core pg. 204",
                        "alt": "Monster Core pg. 204",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
